<h1>Password Reset Request</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.username %>,</p>

<p>You requested a password reset for your Clay Community account.</p>

<p>You can reset your password within the next 20 minutes by clicking the button below:</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= edit_password_url(@user.generate_token_for(:password_reset)) %>" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 14px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;">
    Reset Password
  </a>
</p>

<p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p><%= edit_password_url(@user.generate_token_for(:password_reset)) %></p>

<p><strong>This link will expire in 20 minutes.</strong></p>

<p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email.</p>

<p>Thanks,<br>
The Clay Community Team</p>
